Q: Spring React and Sessions.. how to keep session A: <p>Configure axios to send session cookie back in every request, see below React (JavaScript) example -</p>
<pre><code>import axios from &quot;axios&quot;;

axios.defaults.withCredentials = true; // Send cookies with every request

export const login = async (username) =&gt; {
  return axios.post(
    &quot;http://localhost:8080/api/login&quot;,
    null,
    { params: { username } }
  );
};
</code></pre>

